aring thick black cat-eye glasses, a light blue retro waitress uniform with pale trim, a matching headband, and a name badge. She holds a pen and pad, smiling as she takes an order. The curly-haired young man in the plaid shirt looks up at her from a booth. Behind him are condiment bottles, menus, and other diners. His expression shifts from eager to animated as he speaks, gesturing slightly while looking at her.\n\nIn the kitchen area, a Black male staff member in a white Adidas jacket, seen from behind, opens large stainless-steel refrigerator or freezer doors. The cool interior glows blue, and stacked blue Adidas shoe boxes are visible inside. The diner’s kitchen is metallic and industrial, with storage shelves and equipment around him.\n\nBack at the booth, the curly-haired customer continues talking to the waitress, looking up with wide eyes. The waitress then gives a playful, deliberate reaction: in close-up, she has a small whistle in her mouth, her lips pursed around it. She turns toward a jukebox-style control panel and presses a round button with a red-painted fingernail. The panel has numbered selections including “10,” “11,” “12,” and “13,” and lettered buttons “A,” “B,” “C,” and “D,” reinforcing the retro diner atmosphere.\n\nA blue cooler branded with Adidas-style white stripes is opened. Thick white vapor spills out from inside, as if the contents are chilled on dry ice. The lid lifts to reveal more fog. A Black male employee in a white Adidas jacket looks down into it, framed by stacks of blue Adidas shoe boxes behind him. Inside the cooler, several Adidas shoes are arranged upright in ice like chilled food items: black sneakers with visible trefoil logos and a taller black shoe with bright pink laces and pink lining. The shoes are presented as if they are the diner’s special order.\n\nUnder a booth table, several pairs of Adidas shoes are shown together. A white high-top sneaker with black stripes lifts and moves near another person’s leg; beside it